com.usebottles.bottles (2021.7.28-treviso) precise; urgency=low

  * Support for .lnk files
  * Run any .exe/.msi/.lnk using the flags -e/-l in command line
  * Specify the target bottle using the -b flag in command line
  * Run executables without show the Bottles Window
  * Dependencies can now set register keys
  * Dependencies can now extract archives
  * Dependencies can now uninstall other dependencies
  * Dependencies can now install more dll in one step
  * Dependencies can now register fonts in the Bottle Register to make them discoverable by the runner
  * Cab extraction now support wildcards
  * Cab extraction now support lowercase extensions
  * When installing a new runner, winemenubuilder is blocked to prevent the creation of broken desktop entries
  * The bottle root is now set as the working directory for all executed commands
  * Fixed a bug in the dependency manager showing them installed even though the process was still running
  * Fixed a bug that prevented states from being sent to the bottle (kill, shutdown, reboot, ..)
  * Fixed a bug on processes listing
  * Fix crash log path on Flatpak
  * Fixed an issue causing Bottles to detect downloaded dxvk even when it fails
  * Fixed a bug that cause some programs to not be placed in Programs section
  * Fixed a bug that cause Bottles to crash when a component download fail
  * Uninstallers are now no longer displayed in the Programs list
  * Disable uninstaller button for dependencies installed from cab files
  * Warning for missing cabextract tool
  * Warning for enables testing repository
  * Access Bottles preferences from the bottle creation view
  * A spinner is now displayed when installing dependencies, programs and components
  * Warning for experimental features
  * Several improvements in runner management
  * Added icons to the sidebar
  * Experimantal support for Bottles installers
  * Better support for Breeze theme
  * Browse programs path
  * Generate Bottles compatible desktop entries for programs installed trought Bottles installers
  * Visual feedback during a state restoring
  * Add external executable to the program list
  * Toggle update date on bottles list
  * Chinese (Simplified) translations thanks to @Yuzaihhhh and @sr093906
  * Japanese translations thanks to @jatin-cbs
  * Hungarian translations thanks to @ovari
  * Polish translations thanks to Krzysztof Marcinek
  * French translations thanks to @julroy67
  * Russian translations thanks to @tacitcoast
  * Italian translations thanks to @blackcat-917


